
extends ./layout.pug

block variables
  - var nav_class = 'dark'
  - var activeDoc = page

block body

  -// Content Section
  //div

    -// Display the slices
    //for slice in page.data.body
      case slice.slice_type
        when 'highlight_section'
          include ./slices/highlight-section.pug
        when 'banner'
          include ./slices/banner.pug
        when 'banner_look'
          include ./slices/quote-banner.pug
        when 'editorial_look'
          include ./slices/featured-section.pug
        when 'text_section'
          include ./slices/text-section.pug
        when 'image_slider'
          include ./slices/image-slider.pug 
        when 'gallery'
          include ./slices/gallery.pug
        when 'video'
          include ./slices/video.pug


  // Header
  header
    .block-opacity
      .container
        .intro-text
          p
            | MAKE SURE YOU 
            br
            | HAVE A GREAT HOLIDAY
          p.bordure
          p.text-header
            | WE CAN'T CHOOSE THE DESTINATION FOR YOU! BUT WE CAN GUARANTEE YOU'LL TRAVEL WITH COMPLETE PEACE OF MIND.
          a.page-scroll.btn.btn-xl.btncontact.btntroismois(href='#offres') PRODUCTS
  // Le produit Section
  section#assurance-voyage.bg-light-gray.bloc-voyage
    .container
      .row
        .col-lg-12.text-center
          // <h3 class="large text-muted space-bottom-60 pretitle"></h3>
          h2.section-heading FOYER VOYAGE
          p.text-muted.text-justify
            | Foyer travel insurance offers global coverage which takes into account risks linked to private travel, alone or as a family, no matter the destination or the departure period.
          p.text-muted.text-bold Two travel insurance packages are available
      .row.marketing.block-formule
        .col-lg-3.col-lg-offset-3.col-md-4.col-sm-6.col-md-offset-2.col-xs-12
          .text-formule.block-formule-left
            h4
              b annual
            p ideal if you travel several times a year
        .col-lg-3.col-md-4.col-sm-6.col-xs-12
          .text-formule.block-formule-right
            h4
              b temporary
            p which gives you an all-in-one protection for occasional trips.
  // Les garanties Section
  section#loyergaranti.bg-white-garanties.block-garanties
    .container
      .row
        .col-xs-12.text-center
          h2.section-heading COVER
          p.text-muted.text-Semibold.space-bottom-30 For an optimal protection, Foyer Travel offers you a cover that suits your need!
      .row.marketing
        .col-sm-6.col-lg-5.col-lg-offset-1.col-xs-12
          .block-timeline-bagage
            .timeline-image
              img.img-valise.img-responsive(src='/lp/voyage/img/about/Valise.png', alt='')
            .timeline-panel
              .timeline-heading
                h4 LUGGAGE INSURANCE
              .timeline-body
                p.text-muted
                  | Theft, damage, etc. – if the worst was to happen, you're covered!
                  br
                  |  The cover is applied to the value of the luggage, as well as on cash and valuables!
          .block-timeline-assistance
            .timeline-image
              img.img-assistance.img-responsive(src='/lp/voyage/img/about/Assistance.png', alt='')
            .timeline-panel
              .timeline-heading
                h4 ASSISTANCE
              .timeline-body
                p.text-muted
                  | If something goes wrong, the assistance is guaranteed to you 24 hours a day wherever you are in the world!
                  br
                  |  Early return, loss or theft of your documents, you need money abroad? You can count on your travel insurance!
        .col-sm-6.col-lg-5.col-xs-12
          .block-timeline-annulation
            .timeline-image
              img.img-x.img-responsive(src='/lp/voyage/img/about/X.png', alt='')
            .timeline-panel
              .timeline-heading
                h4 CANCELLATION INSURANCE
              .timeline-body
                p.text-muted
                  | There are many benefits to booking your holiday in advance!
                  br
                  |  With the cancellation cover, you don't need to worry about any last-minute surprises and you can book your next holiday in all serenity!
          .block-timeline-medicaux
            .timeline-image
              img.img-medicaux.img-responsive(src='/lp/voyage/img/about/Frais-medicaux.png', alt='')
            .timeline-panel
              .timeline-heading
                h4 MEDICAL COSTS
              .timeline-body
                p.text-muted
                  | An accident can easily happen, even on vacation. Medical costs, in addition to assistance, covers the expenses incurred abroad.
  // Einfach Fir Iech do -
  section#Einfach.bg-light-blue
    .center-block.text-center
