          h3.foyer-highlight.space-top-20.space-bottom-35 DEFINE YOUR TRAVELLER PROFILE!
          p.text-muted.text-justify
            | Do you travel from time to time, often, all the time? By plane, by boat, by train or by car? Alone, as a family or with friends?
            br
            b Foyer Travel suits your needs!
      .row.bloc-team-member
