            img.img-responsive.img-circle(src='/lp/voyage/img/offers/2-en.jpg', alt='')
            h4 TRAVELLER WITH REEBOU POLICY
            p.text-muted
              span.foyer-highlight.center-block
                | from 
                span.price 7,5€
                | /month
              br
              b Annual travel package
              br
              |  You can add the Travel package to your Reebou policy and benefit of a reduced rate.
            a.page-scroll.btn.btn-xl.frm-presel.btncontratoffres.btnvoyageannuel(href='#contact', data-frm-presel='reebou_family') Interested ?
        .col-sm-4.col-xs-12
          .team-member.center-block
            img.img-responsive.img-circle(src='/lp/voyage/img/offers/3-en.jpg', alt='')
            h4 1 TO 2 TRIPS/YEAR
            p.text-muted
              span.foyer-highlight.center-block Custom quote
              br
              b Temporary policy
              br
              |  It is based on the duration and the price of your trip.
            a.page-scroll.btn.btn-xl.frm-presel.btncontratoffres.btncontrattemporaire(href='#contact', data-frm-presel='assurance_voyage_temp') Receive an offer ?
      //
